                    java.io.IOException
        Parses respond data from MySQL2PHP2Java and put them into columns and values.
        Parameters:
        respond - text generated from PHP script
        calledBy - by which MySQL2PHP2Java instance was this program called
        whereString - That part of SQL statement after word WHERE (e. g. sql = "SELECT * from users WHERE id = 4" -> whereString = "id = 4")
        Throws:
        aho.util.mysql2PHP2Java.exceptions.DatabaseWasNotFoundException
